  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Tiffany Restaurant</strong> is open for breakfast, lunch and dinner and serves local dishes using fresh ingredients in an elegant setting overlooking the garden terrace. Open for breakfast from 7am - 10am, lunch from 12pm - 3:30pm and dinner from 7pm - 10:30pm</p>
<p><strong>Parrucchiano Restaurant </strong>is famous for its cannelloni or 'Strascinati' - the dish invented in Sorrento over 100 years ago. The restaurant has been open since 1868 and its just 200 metres from the hotel on Corso Italia, the main street. It's the perfect place to try traditional food from the Campania region and you'll receive a discount card from the hotel that you can use here. Open for lunch from 12pm - 3pm and dinner from 7pm - 11:30pm</p>
<p><strong>Bellavista Terrace</strong> has views over the Bay of Naples and Mount Vesuvius. The snack bar is a great place for lunch or light refreshments. Open 12pm - 4pm</p>
<p><strong>American Bar</strong> serves cocktails, spirits and local wines in a luxurious lounge area with live music playing five times a week. It's the ideal place for aperitivo.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
