  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>This popular five-star hotel is right in the centre of Sorrento, just a five-minutes from Piazzo Tasso. It has a modern, yet classically <a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italian</a> style with a sophisticated bar and restaurant, plus a rooftop pool with views of the bay.</p>]]></listingDescription>
