  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Rooms </strong><span>are on lower floors and have a balcony or terrace. They are bright and spacious and have tiled floors and wooden furniture. Facilities include a bathtub with a shower, </span>air conditioning, TV, minibar, safe and hairdryer. They can sleep up to three adults.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>have views over the gardens and a balcony. These rooms have high ceilings decorated with beautiful frescoes and a bathtub with a shower. They are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Classic Rooms for single use</strong> are available on request, please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
